title: Prime UES 1BD 1BA, Elevator, Super, Roof Deck, Laundry, Renovated
posting_body: ['1420 York Ave Unit 5H', 'Lenox Hill 1 Bedroom 1 Bath apartment on the 5th floor of an elevator building available for rent starting September 1st 2022.', 'This home has refinished wood floors, an updated kitchen and bath, a ton of storage in unit, and new Midea U-shaped AC unit for more energy efficiency.', 'The bedroom has plenty of room for a queen bed and desk for working from home.', ' You have flexibility to open up the space between the kitchen and living room or bring your portable kitchen island to create separation of space.', ' So many possibilities to put your personal touch on this lovely apartment.', ' Available furnished or unfurnished.', 'Laundry and live in super are available onsite.', ' Enjoy quiet moments on the recently updated roof deck!', 'Walking distance to Central Park, museum mile and all the goodness of the Upper East Side.', ' This is a wonderful place to call home!', '1 or 2 year lease ok.', 'Cats only, no dogs allowed in this building.', 'Showing by appointment only.', 'Contact Cindy at (510)788-0083']
